# Implementation Plan: Full Stack Integration & Real-time Flow

This plan outlines the steps to integrate the `backend-api`, `admin-panel`, and `mobile-user-app` into a fully functional "K-Mart" style hyperlocal application.

## Proposed Changes

### 1. Backend API (Real-time & Data Enrichment)

#### [NEW] [orders.gateway.ts](file:///d:/mart/baldia-mart/backend-api/src/orders/orders.gateway.ts)
- Create a Socket.io gateway to handle real-time order status updates.
- Allow users to join a room specific to their order (e.g., `order_{id}`).

#### [MODIFY] [orders.service.ts](file:///d:/mart/baldia-mart/backend-api/src/orders/orders.service.ts)
- Inject the [OrdersGateway](file:///d:/mart/baldia-mart/backend-api/src/orders/orders.gateway.ts#10-43) to emit status changes when an order is updated (e.g., from `pending` to `confirmed`).

#### [NEW] [seed.controller.ts](file:///d:/mart/baldia-mart/backend-api/src/admin/seed.controller.ts)
- Create an endpoint to populate the database with realistic categories and products (e.g., Snacks, Beverages, Fresh Produce) using placeholder images.

---

### 2. Admin Panel (Management UI)

#### [MODIFY] [categories/page.tsx](file:///d:/mart/baldia-mart/admin-panel/src/app/categories/page.tsx)
- Implement a full CRUD UI for categories.
- Add a modal/form to add a NEW category with name, description, and image URL.

#### [MODIFY] [products/page.tsx](file:///d:/mart/baldia-mart/admin-panel/src/app/products/page.tsx)
- Implement a full CRUD UI for products.
- Link products to categories via a dropdown.

---

### 3. Mobile User App (Integration)

#### [MODIFY] [HomeScreen.tsx](file:///d:/mart/baldia-mart/mobile-user-app/src/screens/HomeScreen.tsx)
- Replace static `CATEGORIES` and `PRODUCTS` constants with API calls.
- Fetch data from `GET /api/v1/categories` and `GET /api/v1/products`.

#### [MODIFY] [CartScreen.tsx](file:///d:/mart/baldia-mart/mobile-user-app/src/screens/CartScreen.tsx)
- Implement functional "Add to Cart" logic (local state management).
- Calculate totals and navigate to Checkout.

#### [MODIFY] [CheckoutScreen.tsx](file:///d:/mart/baldia-mart/mobile-user-app/src/screens/CheckoutScreen.tsx)
- Connect "Place Order" button to `POST /api/v1/orders/checkout`.
- Handle success by navigating to an order tracking view.

#### [NEW] [OrderTrackingScreen.tsx](file:///d:/mart/baldia-mart/mobile-user-app/src/screens/OrderTrackingScreen.tsx)
- Display current order status.
- Listen for Socket.io events to update status in real-time.

